=============================================================================
PngDataGen : Tool for generating 1x1 pixel transparent PNGs as data uris
Copyright (c) 2012 Owain Cleaver
Released under the terms of GNU GPL version 3; see COPYING
=============================================================================

Windows application for generating 1x1 pixel PNG data uris from CSS3 argb()
function syntax.

Apparently this is useful for getting around IE8's lack of argb() support.

Requirements:
 - Windows
 - .net Framework 4 (Client profile)
 
Binary download : http://www.lor3.org/crap/PngDataGen.zip

kthxbye